{"tid":248120,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【高C9手記】國泰大裁員 公關部重災(高淑嫻)","createTime":"2017-05-18T10:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T12:23:37.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2120b9f222cd16576b7422a17e378ebb7d230a1c","tid":248120,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170518/large/1495098614_21b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170518%2Flarge%2F1495098614_21b8.jpg&h=27b6a8a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全世界都知道國泰航空(293)要大裁員，唯獨3,000名後勤及中高層過去數月蒙在鼓裏，由1月公司宣佈計劃重組開始，分分鐘要等到下周一，才由最高層發落，這個裁員行動認真慘無人道，完全不理會漫長等待，對員工帶來的心理壓力。<br />\n<br />\n聽講，由於公司決定削減成本30%，基本上每個部門都要交人，公關部門也是重災區之一，負責整體公關策劃的企業事務董事一職將會刪去，之下4名經理最終可能只得一位有得留低，職級較低的同事亦不能倖免。<br />\n<br />\n可能有人認為，一間企業進行大重組，風雨飄搖之際，最需要就是公關向市場解話，無理由如此大刀闊斧減人，偏偏這個case未必用在國泰身上。客觀而論，國泰過去四、五年，有公關等於無公關，管理層似乎完全不理會企業形象插水，沒有推動公關部門打一場漂亮的仗，面對網民及傳媒負評，只處於捱打或I don&rsquo;t care狀態。<br />\n<br />\n不過，此爛攤子肯定不是由公關部孭晒，管理層要負上最大責任。君不見許多機構的主席或行政總裁相當重視公關及企業形象，一出事即刻指揮大局，甚至飛身出來撲火。<br />\n<br />\n又正如公關界前輩所講，最上乘的公關，不是等到出事時，如何拆招，而是事先預計晒出事位，做好防火準備，根本不會讓關公災難發生。可惜，有些管理層偏偏喜歡自製關公災難，然後向公關同事問責。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56710825&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170518\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56710825%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170518&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=6682aeb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56710825%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170518&h=bc4bcd9b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56710825&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170518</a>"},{"pid":"df0c78b42a3ff179d32ca38b494932c439f774f5","tid":248120,"uid":29008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:35:06.000Z","msg":"是鳩但啦，一減價你班撚樣咪照坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d064912c50ba009ce8da4a62c29e7229444a96","tid":248120,"uid":83654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是鳩但啦，一減價你班撚樣咪照坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n經營航空公司之道就係當Econ 客係猪咁運<br />\n大把老一輩港猪只信KA, CX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n后生既坐開廉航既坐次CX 仲唔打晒卡<br />\n服務差？ CX 推少少優惠咪又狗衝"},{"pid":"1c8e66a60e9da04f7e74a1515583416064868e9c","tid":248120,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:05:25.000Z","msg":"炒曬啲無謂人減價仲實際"},{"pid":"9e1ec4281d9a7745031b96e1bb8c37701d699a88","tid":248120,"uid":66157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:07:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>炒曬啲無謂人減價仲實際</blockquote><br />\n咁會冇高層去買油對賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030c82232ac2530c2942de691d7faf38c311076c","tid":248120,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:23:37.000Z","msg":"工作上接觸過國泰 managerial grade <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八個字：架構臃腫、冗員太多"}]}